# Server Folder Rules
- Use **SQLModel** (built on SQLAlchemy) for models in `server/app/models.py` as the canonical schema; update them whenever the DB schema changes.
- All business logic belongs in **`server/app/services/`**; keep route handlers in `server/app/routes/` thin.
- Enforce **100% passing `pytest`** (`make test`) before merge.
- Run **`make typecheck`** (mypy) and **`make lint`** (ruff) locally; fix or silence any errors with clear justification.
- Use **`uv`** for dependency management and virtual environment handling.
- Follow **12-factor config**: secrets via env vars, no hard-coded credentials.
- Prefer async endpoints when possible; use **SQLModel Session** for DB access.
- Auto-generate models from DB schema using `make generate-models`.
